SAN FRANCISCO GIANTS (BASEBALL TEAM); CHICAGO CUBS (BASEBALL TEAM); BOSTON RED 
SOX (BASEBALL TEAM); PITTSBURGH PIRATES (BASEBALL TEAM); NEW YORK METS 
(BASEBALL TEAM); TORONTO BLUE JAYS (BASEBALL TEAM); BALTIMORE ORIOLES (BASEBALL 
TEAM); MONTREAL EXPOS (BASEBALL TEAM) 
</P>
