be selected a second-team All-American by one wire service last season. Alfred 
Williams (above) was a first-team choice. ; Photo, Alfred Williams, pictured 
playing against Nebraska, had 10 1/2 sacks, 14 quarterback hurries and five 
pass deflections last season. ; Photo, (Orange County Edition) COLOR, Alfred 
