STRATEGY; AMERICANS -- MIDDLE EAST; IRAQ -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- KUWAIT; 
MILITARY CONFRONTATIONS; UNITED STATES -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- IRAQ; IRAQ -- 
ARMED FORCES -- KUWAIT; UNITED STATES -- ARMED FORCES -- SAUDI ARABIA; 
AMERICANS -- IRAQ; AMERICANS -- KUWAIT; UNITED STATES -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- 
MIDDLE EAST 
</P>
